METHODS:
constructor(string text): make window + show Menu 			-> show map options at startup (menu Text must be given)
public void loadMap(string fileName)					-> load chosen map after startup
public void drawMap(2D-Array troops)					-> draw new Map after a change (includes the troops + possible positions)
public void setText(int pos, string color, string text)			-> set text at a specific position on screen
public void removeText(int pos)						-> delete text at a specific position
public char getTerrain(int x, int y)					-> return the terrain at the given position
destructor: kill window

VALUES:
2D-Array map 
List texts
